Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.56,INC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you 也能相通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:08.40,INC,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,100)}Follow me Follow you 无论多么遥远
